snippet.title: NeonAether
snippet.description:
We are on an intergalactic space voyage exploring the unknown, heading towards a dying Neon Sun. Can you feel the Aether...?

Welcome, traveller! We are a channel dedicated to the revival of the synthwave genre, featuring all music synthwave, darkwave, cyberwave and everything inbetween retro, newretro and 80s. We are a channel inspired by the lifestyle, feel and sounds of the era and would gladly welcome you aboard our intergalactic vessel, the S.S. Synthwave on our maiden voyage! Our dedicated subscribers, we are grateful to have you with us!

If you are interested in sharing your music on the channel, please email us at the address below with a full quality audio track, album art and social media links!

If you like the page, consider supporting us by subscribing, sharing and liking the videos we upload. We also have a Patreon page below if you are interested in enabling us to put more resources into growing the channel and uploading more content.

Over and out, 

~ NeonAether
